It s from Turkey, Trabzon. You cant reach this studio, coz', most likely it s close. The studio's name is Görçek Studio and the word of "Görçek" was using 1940s. In those years, there were lots of Görçek Foto Studios in Turkey. This name was so popular during those years. "Görçek" meant "selfie" (: As a result, neither studio name nor address are unhelpful in order to find photografer. Sorry :(
